ASABA –  The President, “Eco 4 Good Governance Int’l”, Comrade Rufus Onyibe has congratulated Governor Ifeanyi Okowa on his emergence as PDP’s Vice Presidential Candidate, Atiku’s running mate for the forthcoming 2023 general elections in Nigeria. Comrade Rufus Onyibe who doubles as the Special Assistant to Governor Ifeanyi Okowa on Political Matters disclosed this in a press release made available to some group of Journalists today being on Sunday, 26th day of June, 2022 as group commends Governor Ifeanyi Okowa on his emergence as PDP Vice Presidential Candidate. The Governor’s aide has on 23rd of June, 2022 joined the mammoth crowd of Deltans, Nigerians to give heroic welcome and Celebrate the home coming of His Excellency, Sen. Dr. Arthur Ifeanyi Okowa as he congratulated him on his emergence as the party’s choice of running mate to Alhaji Atiku Abubakar. He stated further that the fact that Governor Ifeanyi Okowa was chosen, considered as first among equals, amongst other contestants in the PDP’s Vice Presidential Candidate is a clear indication of his wider acceptability, administration’s developmental strides and exceptional leadership qualities noticeable in Delta State, Niger-Delta region, Southern Nigeria and the country in general. In the words of the President, ECO FOR GOOD GOVERNANCE INT’L, Comrade Rufus Onyibe: “We congratulate our amiable Governor, His Excellency, Senator (Dr.)Arthur Ifeanyi Okowa on his emergence as the PDP Vice Presidential Candidate for the 2023 general elections in Nigeria”. “Our party PDP has made very good choice by nominating Governor Ifeany Okowa for the Vice Presidential Running Mate position. Our amiable Governor is a competent political leader, an intelligent, articulate and a very focus, humble, Youth-friendly, accessible, hardworking and loyal party man”.